VUCA world
	V - Volatile
	U - Uncertain
	C - Complex
	A - Ambiguous

Psychologist Daniel Goleman identified five elements that make up emotional intelligence. These are:
	Self-awareness.
	Self-regulation.
	Motivation.
	Empathy.
	Social skills.

Goleman's Model	
	Self-awareness
	Social-awareness
	Self-management
	Relationship management

